Like the other [[steward roles|XSCALE Stewards]], product steward is a [[Servant Leader]] accountable for making decisions when the [[Product Squad]] cannot reach consensus in decisions about feature definitions, [[Acceptance Criteria]] and [[Royal Cod]] priorities. The product steward is also responsible for answering [[Delivery Squad]] questions about features and stories when the [[Product Squad]] isn't conveniently available.